<headline>Heat Advisory issued July 24 at 3:01AM CDT until July 24 at 8:00PM CDT by NWS Amarillo</headline>
<description>...HEAT ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 1 PM THIS AFTERNOON TO 8 PM CDT THIS
EVENING...
* WHAT...High temperatures of 106 expected.
* WHERE...Palo Duro Canyon State Park.
* WHEN...From 1 PM this afternoon to 8 PM CDT this evening.
* IMPACTS...Hot temperatures may cause heat illnesses.</description>
<instruction>Drink plenty of fluids, stay in an air-conditioned room, stay out of
the sun, and check up on relatives and neighbors.</instruction>
